name: proj-offliner
description: Project off-liner. Gets some Google appSript project's json-file, converts it to object,selects appropriated project parts' files  array from jsonObj.files property, parses each element content and saves as separate js-file into specified temporary folder on local PC. Assembles js files editted into new project json file ready for uploading
author: Vladimir Uralov <v.url.node@gmail.com>
